This paper involves the use of natural language processing techniques to extract meaningful tokens from job postings data, which suggests that it could belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of AI-powered job search engines, which could fall under the Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) and Deep Learning (cs.DL) sub-categories. The paper also involves the use of databases and APIs to link company names to their respective attributes, which could fall under the Database (cs.DB) sub-category. Finally, the paper mentions the potential for networking opportunities, which could fall under the Cybersecurity (cs.CY) sub-category.
